PersonalizationApplets.source: WHERE APPLET_NAME IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N')

WHERE CT_APPLET_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_CT_APPLET WHERE  APPLET_NAME IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N')) AND CT_RULE_SET_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_CT_RULE_SET)
PersonalizationApplets.target: WHERE CT_APPLET_ID NOT IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_CT_APPLET)

ValidationRule.source: WHERE VALDN_ACTN_ID IN (SELECT VA.ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_ACTN VA, $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RULE VRL, $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RL_SET VRLS WHERE VA.VALDN_RULE_ID=VRL.ROW_ID AND VRL.RULE_SET_ID=VRLS.ROW_ID AND VRLS.STATUS_CD='Active')

WHERE VALDN_RULE_ID IN (SELECT VRL.ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RULE VRL, $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RL_SET VRLS WHERE VRL.RULE_SET_ID=VRLS.ROW_ID AND VRLS.STATUS_CD='Active') AND (BUSCOMP_NAME IS NULL OR BUSCOMP_NAME IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N'))
WHERE RULE_SET_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RL_SET WHERE STATUS_CD='Active')

WHERE RULE_SET_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VALDN_RL_SET WHERE STATUS_CD='Active') AND (BUSCOMP_NAME IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N'))

WHERE STATUS_CD='Active' AND (BUSCOMP_NAME IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N'))

EAI Data Map.source: WHERE INT_COMP_MAP_ID IN (SELECT ICM.ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_INT_COMPMAP ICM, $TABLEOWNER.S_INT_OBJMAP IOM WHERE ICM.INT_OBJ_MAP_ID=IOM.ROW_ID)

FINS Data Map.source: WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP ) OR ROW_ID IN (SELECT PAR_BC_DMAP_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP ))

WHERE BC_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP) OR ROW_ID IN (SELECT PAR_BC_DMAP_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP)))

WHERE BUSCOMP_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP ) OR ROW_ID IN (SELECT PAR_BC_DMAP_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP )))

WHERE FIELD_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_FIELD_DMAP WHERE BUSCOMP_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP) OR ROW_ID IN (SELECT PAR_BC_DMAP_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP_DMAP WHERE BUSOBJ_DMAP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSOBJ_DMAP))))

nodes.SQL: SELECT APPLET_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_CT_APPLET WHERE APPLET_NAME NOT IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APPLET WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N')

SELECT BUSCOMP_NAME, RESTRICTION_CD, TO_CHAR(FROM_TZ(CAST(START_DT AS TIMESTAMP), 'GMT') at time zone 'US/Eastern', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS AUDIT_START FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AUDIT_BUSCOMP T2 WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N' AND T1.NAME = T2.BUSCOMP_NAME)

SELECT ADM1.BUSCOMP_NAME AS BUSCOMP_NAME, ADM1.RESTRICTION_CD AS RESTRICTION_CD, TO_CHAR(FROM_TZ(CAST(START_DT AS TIMESTAMP), 'GMT') at time zone 'US/Eastern', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS AUDIT_START, ADM2.FIELD_NAME AS FIELD_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AUDIT_BUSCOMP ADM1, $TABLEOWNER.S_AUDIT_FIELD ADM2 WHERE ADM2.AUDIT_BC_ID = ADM1.ROW_ID AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ( $WORKSPACE_QUERY )) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_BUSCOMP WHERE ( $WORKSPACE_QUERY )) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1, (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_FIELD WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_FIELD WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T2 WHERE T2.BUSCOMP_ID = T1.WS_SRC_ID AND T2.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N' AND T2.INACTIVE_FLG='N' AND T1.NAME= ADM1.BUSCOMP_NAME AND T2.NAME=ADM2.FIELD_NAME)

SELECT T2.NAME AS TMPL_NAME, T2.TYPE_CD AS TMPL_TYPE, T4.LINE_NUM FROM SIEBEL.S_INT_INSTANCE T1,SIEBEL.S_TMPL_PLANITEM T2,SIEBEL.S_USER T3,SIEBEL.S_EVT_TASK T4,SIEBEL.S_PARTY T5,SIEBEL.S_EVT_ACT_SS T6,SIEBEL.S_EVT_ACT T7 WHERE  T7.TMPL_PLANITEM_ID = T2.ROW_ID (+) AND T6.OWN_INST_ID = T1.ROW_ID (+) AND T7.ROW_ID = T4.PAR_ROW_ID (+) AND T7.ROW_ID = T6.PAR_ROW_ID (+) AND T7.OWNER_PER_ID = T5.ROW_ID (+) AND T7.OWNER_PER_ID = T3.PAR_ROW_ID (+) AND (T7.TEMPLATE_FLG = 'Y') AND (T7.TMPL_PLANITEM_ID IN (SELECT T2.ROW_ID  FROM SIEBEL.S_CL_PTCL_LS T1,SIEBEL.S_TMPL_PLANITEM T2 WHERE  T2.CL_PTCL_ID = T1.ROW_ID (+) AND (T2.TMPL_TYPE_CD = 'Activity' AND T2.TYPE_CD != 'Clinical Subject') AND (T2.TYPE_CD = 'Account'))) GROUP BY T2.NAME, T2.TYPE_CD, T4.LINE_NUM  HAVING COUNT(T4.LINE_NUM)>1

nodes.SQL: SELECT DISTINCT NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW WHERE NAME NOT IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N')

preimpsql.DELETE_APP_VIEW: DELETE FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW WHERE ROW_ID IN (SELECT VIEW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW_RESP AVP, SIEBEL.S_RESP RSP WHERE AVP.RESP_ID =RSP.ROW_ID) AND ROW_ID NOT IN (SELECT VIEW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW_RESP AVP, $TABLEOWNER.S_RESP RSP WHERE AVP.RESP_ID =RSP.ROW_ID )

nodes.SQL: SELECT DISTINCT RSP.NAME AS RESP_NAME, AV.NAME AS VIEW_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW_RESP AVR, $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW AV, $TABLEOWNER.S_RESP RSP WHERE (AVR.VIEW_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW WHERE NAME NOT IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N'))) AND AVR.VIEW_ID=AV.ROW_ID AND AVR.RESP_ID=RSP.ROW_ID

SELECT DISTINCT RSP.NAME AS RESP_NAME, AV.NAME AS VIEW_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW_RESP AVR, $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW AV, $TABLEOWNER.S_RESP RSP WHERE (AVR.VIEW_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_APP_VIEW WHERE NAME NOT IN (SELECT T1.NAME FROM (SELECT TBL1.* FROM (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL1 LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_VIEW WHERE ($WORKSPACE_QUERY)) TBL2 ON (TBL1.WS_SRC_ID = TBL2.WS_SRC_ID AND TBL1.WS_OBJ_VER < TBL2.WS_OBJ_VER) WHERE TBL2.WS_SRC_ID IS NULL AND TBL1.WS_DELETE_FLG = 'N') T1 WHERE T1.REPOSITORY_ID = $REPOSITORY_ID AND T1.INACTIVE_FLG='N'))) AND AVR.VIEW_ID=AV.ROW_ID AND AVR.RESP_ID=RSP.ROW_ID

SELECT DISTINCT AR.NAME AS TASK_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AC_RSRC_RESP ARR, $TABLEOWNER.S_AC_RSRC AR, $TABLEOWNER.S_RESP RSP WHERE ARR.RSRC_ID=AR.ROW_ID AND ARR.RESP_ID=RSP.ROW_ID  AND ARR.RSRC_ID NOT IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AC_RSRC WHERE TYPE_CD='TASK' AND NAME IN (SELECT TBL2.TASK_NAME FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_TU_TASK TBL2, (SELECT TASK_NAME, MAX(VERSION) MAXVER FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_TU_TASK WHERE REPOSITORY_ID= $REPOSITORY_ID AND INACTIVE_FLG='N' GROUP BY TASK_NAME) TBL1 WHERE TBL1.TASK_NAME = TBL2.TASK_NAME AND TBL1.MAXVER = TBL2.VERSION AND TBL2.STATUS_CD='COMPLETED' AND TBL2.REPOSITORY_ID= $REPOSITORY_ID))

preimpsql.DELETE_RSRC_RESP: DELETE FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AC_RSRC_RESP WHERE RESP_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_RESP) AND RSRC_ID IN (SELECT ROW_ID FROM $TABLEOWNER.S_AC_RSRC WHERE TYPE_CD='TASK')
